    Incompatible with QWS_DEPTH_8GRAYSCALE.

<tr><td valign=top>QT_NO_QWS_DEPTH_15 <td valign=top>
    15-bit-per-pixel - 32 levels each of Red, Blue, and Green.

<tr><td valign=top>QT_NO_QWS_DEPTH_16 <td valign=top>
